description:
so much connecting the two.. it seams they are trying to get us in our homes so they can turn up the smart meters on the side of all our houses. not to mention 5g still going up while we’re all being kept inside, watching our television to stay updated on the “virus” they are telling us not to be so scared of though it’s all they are talking about and everything else is cancelled so the public almost has no choice but to watch. my advice to anyone is to stay prepared to have to leave in the event of something happening like martial law, be aware, be cautious but most importantly remain calm and don’t let this chaos create fear inside of you. there is a mass shift happening world wide, can you feel it ? •
